text: Nice mini mart, all basic home appliances and groceries available. A section for a wet floor also in good way and clean mean the arrangement is well planned.
Just open for a few month. Still lacking product sells inside the shop. Recently shops there, cannot find maggi 1 pack.
Vegetables and prawns are fresh. Dry food not much choice. Service is good
Always went here to buy my cat's food... Affordable price.. Well nothing cheaper nowadays right?...
